| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0076 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 17a9a813-2196-5986-85e7-f79b8037b9e7"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
